e":"2021-02-21T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"移民囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fac1d3dd51d6d050e7c748fec133b7ae89f60a","tid":2416731,"uid":292111,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2416899/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2416899/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以先睇以下ig post了解件事🙏🙏<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLi-K4ZFjTK/?igshid=mtcg2ynoe62z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLi-K4ZFjTK%2F%3Figshid%3Dmtcg2ynoe62z&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=0dfa17d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLi-K4ZFjTK%2F%3Figshid%3Dmtcg2ynoe62z&h=3c158ffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CLi-K4ZFjTK/?igshid=mtcg2ynoe62z</a><br />\n【勇武娃原創者 希望大家一齊守護本土文化】<br />\n香港人鎖匙扣（勇武娃）是本人獨自一人的設計創作品，第一次出現是在2019年9月，自此本人從來沒有將產品寄賣，亦沒有授權過任何第三方售賣。<br />\n然而, 在2020年12月，本人發現有多間店鋪 同1仔冰室合作售賣一款 與本人設計相似程度極高的公仔。 <br />\n我早於2020年12月發現並出post指出該公仔是本人原創，沒有授權寄賣。 <br />\n本人明白相關店鋪原意是為了支持手足, 所以曾嘗試聯絡有關店鋪, 希望對方可以尊重原創，如果繼續售賣有關作品以支持手足, 請credit原創者，<br />\n但直到現在他們一直沒有正面回應我的提問和要求, 並持續於年宵和新春市集繼續販賣與本人作品高度相似的作品。 <br />\n本人現公開呼籲以下相關店鋪,&nbsp; 請尊重創作者, 你的善意很可能不小心扼殺了我們的生存空間,<br />\n香港文化, 本土意識 全靠大家一起守護 <br />\n有關店鋪: <br />\nAngel's Paradise<br />\n1仔冰室<br />\n&amp; 相關合作店鋪<br />\n因為大家有著相同出發點, 本人至今沒向相關店鋪索取任何賠償, 只是希望作品能加回應有的原作者資料 (credit),<br />\n但若情況持續, 本人保留一切追究權利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><br />\n我係真正鎖匙扣原創者，唔信既話其實睇下post既各個日期就知道<br />\n另外1仔冰室已經今日pm左我，另一方面證實左我係原創<br />\n但尼間售賣店鋪出post抹黑我，話我騷擾佢地，話我&ldquo;自稱原創者&rdquo;<br />\n希望大家可以幫幫我:sob::sob:&nbsp; <br />\n我只係2月8日pm過佢地一次但受到佢地無視，佢地繼續擺年宵，無奈之下本人之後搵黃色文創圈同對方溝通，因為有幫手，佢地先至答應停售，原本我講佢地係無視我<br />\n希望大家可以幫幫我:pray::pray:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEuaZ4k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEuaZ4k.jpg&h=62aaa18b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家可以幫幫我，查明真相🙏<br />\n唔好比人借黃搵食<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b3f03ad0350bb44ed6dea6a3299a061998de2b63","tid":2416731,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"過多兩日叫人諗清楚打咩疫苗都變紫旗"},{"pid":"5f59b37df560cc5bcc487ad653883c8050923a75","tid":2416731,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67cf1a0e496526d86dafdd7b66fc264bf99de7ed","tid":2416731,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"372c48fbda4846382906dbadf2146342e3d9a2c8","tid":2416731,"uid":51583,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:09:37.000Z","msg":"仲有勇者敢企咁前<br />\n自愧不如<br />\n唔知可以幫佢地D咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"移民囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"香港人最叻<br />\n睇隔離post都睇得出人心最醜惡"},{"pid":"24e57a49721b450f1317c1dcafd3537a8686a53f","tid":2416731,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0a381f297dec5f38c04b18f8a151c552b5a7c5","tid":2416731,"uid":201605,"like":98,"dislike":5,"score":93,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"班曱甴除咗識搞細路仲識啲乜嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"販冰冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a5e3eb3f74808b595dc4fc89090f19919524ce","tid":2416731,"uid":306689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"留得青山在那怕無柴燒，希望佢哋保重身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5b6de14b2a593b23768f139560eea410b505ec","tid":2416731,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"bcc69257d650322ee4f10f500473451e992e42ce","tid":2416731,"uid":225117,"like":